Hi liencf,

Just a quick reminder - we=E2=80=99re launching Trolley as Topcoder=E2=80=
=99s new global payment platform in one week!

Go-live: Tuesday, Oct 21, 2025, at 02:00 AM ET

Expected transition time: approximately 3 hours

During this window, payments will be temporarily unavailable while we compl=
ete the switch.

What=E2=80=99s Changing

=E2=80=A2  All Topcoder payments will be processed through Trolley.

=E2=80=A2  Payoneer and Paypal will no longer be supported for new payouts =
(You=E2=80=99ll still have access to your existing funds in Payoneer or Pay=
Pal =E2=80=94 they just won=E2=80=99t receive new payments from Topcoder af=
ter October 21).

Note: Your Topcoder wallet balance will remain unchanged and you can still =
withdraw your payment after setting up Trolley.

What You=E2=80=99ll Be Able to Use

=E2=80=A2 Bank transfer (local or international)

What You Need to Do

=E2=80=A2 No action needed right now.

=E2=80=A2 On October 21, you=E2=80=99ll receive an email with instructions =
to set up your Trolley payout method in the Topcoder Wallet App. Setup only=
 takes a few minutes.

