<p style=3D"line-height:175%"><span style=3D"font-weight: bold; color: #0a0=
a0a;">What=E2=80=99s Changing</span><br><span style=3D"color: #0a0a0a;">=E2=
=80=A2&nbsp; All Topcoder payments will be processed through Trolley.</span=
></p>
<p style=3D"line-height:175%"><span style=3D"color: #0a0a0a;">=E2=80=A2&nbs=
p; Payoneer and Paypal will no longer be supported for new payouts (<em>You=
=E2=80=99ll still have access to your existing funds in Payoneer or PayPal =
=E2=80=94 they just won=E2=80=99t receive new payments from Topcoder after =
October 21</em>).</span></p>
