=3D"font-weight: normal;">Note</span>: Your Topcoder wallet balance will re=
main unchanged and you can still withdraw your payment after setting up Tro=
lley.</span></p>
<p style=3D"line-height:175%">&nbsp;</p>
<p style=3D"line-height:175%"><span style=3D"font-weight: bold; color: #0a0=
a0a;">What You=E2=80=99ll Be Able to Use</span><br><span style=3D"color: #0=
a0a0a;">=E2=80=A2 Bank transfer (local or international)</span></p>
<p style=3D"line-height:175%">&nbsp;</p>
<p style=3D"line-height:175%"><span style=3D"font-weight: bold; color: #0a0=
a0a;">What You Need to Do</span><br><span style=3D"color: #0a0a0a;">=E2=80=
=A2 No action needed right now.</span></p>
<p style=3D"line-height:175%"><span style=3D"color: #0a0a0a;">=E2=80=A2 On =
October 21, you=E2=80=99ll receive an email with instructions to set up you=
r Trolley payout method in the Topcoder Wallet App. Setup only takes a few =
